<h2 style="color: #343434;"><strong><i>Chateaux du Monde is uniquely positioned to serve the needs and support the fundraising objectives of community charities and private charitable foundations.Â  Our model rejuvenates existing auction events while establishing new opportunities with Wine Charity Auction. Chateaux du Monde has created an assortment of enhanced experiences for charitable fundraising. We feature access through a broad array of Chateaux du Monde supported charitable fund raising efforts and donor incentive programs, generating significant sustainable donations. Our estate experiences provide rare excitement during live auctions, as feature above in the magnificent 4,500-acre estate property in the heart of Italyâs Tuscan countryside. Private donors face numerous challenges to formulate their personal strategy for local community, national, and global charitable gifts. Chateaux du Monde offers donors a way to ensure their legacy and leverage of charitable support for their chosen charities.Â </i></strong></h2>
<h2 style="color: #343434;"></h2>
<h2><strong><i>Chateaux du Monde provides charitable event fundraising support</i><i>, with proven digital and social marketing strategies, customized email communications with the most current and relevant technology tools normally out of reach to charities. Chateaux du Monde designs, creates, and produces, themed travel experiences, using tailored videos, music, regional wines, with matching regional cuisine with event themes. Auction items are offered through Chateaux du Monde unique relationship with an assortment of brand names and private labeled products.</i></strong></h2>
