<p>As an Investor/Donor of Chateaux du Monde a Foundation dramatically, yet cost-effectively increases their ability to support the fund raising efforts of the charities they support. This is achieved through access to unique and culturally authentic estate properties, and meaningful donor communications support services that combine to result in greater Foundation impact and effectiveness. Foundations become Investors in Chateaux du Monde with exclusive access to estate properties located in the worldâs most exclusive and exotic locals. Foundations may use, or allow others to use the estate properties to create unparalleled experiences for individuals and charitable organizations that, in turn, can make access to such events available through auctions, special donations, and to host events for influential donors and other thought leaders. In addition, Foundations can rely on unique and extraordinary educational support, offered by Chateaux du Mondeâs The Center for Change &amp; Education, to develop and produce events, summits, and symposia focusing on key issues.</p>
<p>Tangible Benefits/Services â for Foundations: CDM Estate Services:</p>
