<li>A 5 star hotel management group. All staff are trained and highly qualified.</li>
<li>Specifically designed suites, ranging in size from 800 to 2,400 Square Feet. All suites have separate living rooms. All bathrooms are master baths, with 2 sinks, stand aline bathing tubs and separate showers.</li>
<li>Suites designed with private and secure access.</li>
<li>Suites with daily maid and nightly turn â down services.</li>
<li>Suites with 24 hour concierge services on site.</li>
