<li>Additional suites available for Foundation principles, staff and additional guests, as needed (addition fee)</li>
<li>On-property access to a large range of amenities, including a spa, a winery, a culinary institute, golf, tennis, polo, hiking and equestrian trails.</li>
<li>Specific reservation protocol for Foundations, Charities and their exclusive donor guests.</li>
<li><strong>Twice Gifted</strong>: Chateaux du Monde returns the foundationsâs initial Investment (at the dissolution of the partnership), which can then be donated to the Foundationsâs designated charity (or charities). At dissolution of the partnership the Foundation donation/investment is returned and can be donated again to the Foundationâs designated charity/charities.</li>
